      <br> <strong>MALDIVERNE: </strong> Dhiffushi <br>
      <br> <strong>SRI LANKA: </strong> Dambulla, Kandy, Ella & Weligama <br>
      <br> <strong>INDONESIEN: </strong> Bali & Gili Islands <br>
      <br> <strong>JAPAN: </strong> Tokyo, Kyoto, Hiroshima, Osak & Nara <br>
      <br> <strong>AUSTRALIEN: </strong> Byron Bay</Text>
